title: Neroche - Discography
description: Couldn't find any torrents for Neroche anywhere, so I ripped them using ClipConverter.cc from the Neroche Official YouTube channel. Included are his 5 album releases: The Crooked Mile, Tryptamine, Elixir, In The Woods...They Wait!, and Roadside Oddities. The bit rate is between 224 and 320 depending on the album and they are in .mp3 format. I just recently discovered Neroche and I am hooked. All of his music is incredible. Hope you guys enjoy it. The music genre is Trip-Hop
